	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Banshaku recently <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?p=114499#p114499" class="postlink">expressed interest in translating the wiki into Japanese</a>. The first step toward this is installing <a href="https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Manual:Wiki_family" class="postlink">wiki family</a> infrastructure to make &quot;ja.wiki.nesdev.com&quot;.

		

		</td>
