	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I can't help with the Japanese translation, but I have many friends who do professional level Japanese translation (including one who works for Nikon doing technical document translation). I think most of the folks I know would need to be paid for their time though.

		

		</td>
